" Shows tags while using Taggit gem.
command ShowTags /<\([A-Z]\+\)>.\{-}<\/\1>

vmap <leader>mp S<PERSON>
vmap <leader>mo S<ORGANIZATION>
vmap <leader>ml S<LOCATION>
vmap <leader>me S<EVENT>
vmap <leader>md S<DATE>
vmap <leader>mt S<TIME>
vmap <leader>mm S<MONEY>
vmap <leader>m% S<PERCENT>
vmap <leader>mq S<QUANTITY>
